data.description: Stunning two-story home in ideal location close (but not TOO close) to restaurants, shopping, and major roadways. The backyard overlooks the preserve and is perfect for entertaining with a custom outdoor kitchen, screened lanai, custom Pergola, pavers, shed and more! Stainless Steel Gourmet kitchen with gas 5 burner cooktop, granite countertops, and HUGE walk-in pantry. Extras include wood-look tile, built-in speakers, and water softener.  The owner's Suite has double sinks with granite countertops, frameless walk-in shower, and separate soaking tub. PAID Solar Panels for significant savings! Check out the document and make your showing appointment today!
